{"tid":979710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國考報名平台冧Server影響70萬考生","createTime":"2019-01-13T02:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T05:57:42.000Z","uid":37554,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"65facf0d81e9ee7169b3f91bd5f68b49ac2af597","tid":979710,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"每年1月上旬，都是內地各大藝術高校藝術類高考報名的時節。然而，作為中央美術學院、中國美術學院、四川美術學院等內地「八大美術學院」唯一報名管道，一款名為「藝術升」的藝考報名App，竟在關鍵時刻「冧Server」，波及70萬考生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/1-11/p2339972a45274469-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F1-11%2Fp2339972a45274469-ss.jpg&h=94706d07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先是報名費，所有人報名，需要先交30元的肖像審核費。<br />\n這個審核，最遲也是三天，慢點一個月都有可能。<br />\n想要快點審核，就要再交50元加急審核費。<br />\n額外繳費可獲「加急審核」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/1-11/p2339974a787522691-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F1-11%2Fp2339974a787522691-ss.jpg&h=833bbddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，查找院校還要交幾百蚊。<br />\n查一個學校就要58蚊，考生一般都要查三四個。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/1-11/p2339975a403207919-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F1-11%2Fp2339975a403207919-ss.jpg&h=918d542f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外報考系統經常崩潰，要想不崩潰，交600快開闢綠色通道。<br />\n我直接懷疑，那些在系統大崩潰中，還能成功報名的人，多半都是VIP客戶吧。<br />\n<br />\n沒交錢的考生，如果去諮詢人工客服。<br />\n那只會得到一句「滾」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/1-11/p2339976a543554093-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F1-11%2Fp2339976a543554093-ss.jpg&h=e7f0c625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53a22d55a4fe1567cbcd8cd2568895f1a0dd2a9f","tid":979710,"uid":37358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:19:51.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"9e684395d2ff9dbbd2f2abf0202b81df57e4d39d","tid":979710,"uid":17765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"支那唔係好撚先進？"},{"pid":"67c98856a486b50b243dd542171f6908519bc1ab","tid":979710,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"男盗女娼, 支那整容雞po自己張閃卡應該連錢都唔駛畀"},{"pid":"89737ff51a91a0f3394e90c736bb17e3c2c1c771","tid":979710,"uid":37586,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"報名考試都玩vip呢個國家痴撚線，不如公開直接買分算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488236cd10afbcc3eed8e9a73ae3e0f0f6429a7b","tid":979710,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"a16437fb0f8306f7878548eb646148775d8fb479","tid":979710,"uid":2002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"課金入U 牛B死了"},{"pid":"b9c6629f8570f9b0225ef2bdb916e97b1aa85ca5","tid":979710,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1642156221b343f9be96321ccade2d569cdc9750","tid":979710,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"中國特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac33e2068561a52ab1e7bc0e5409f581292efc69","tid":979710,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89737ff51a91a0f3394e90c736bb17e3c2c1c771","tid":979710,"uid":37586,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:31:40.000Z","msg